{
  "texts": [
    "In any case, we should store different stages for future reuse.",
    "In the first part of this article, we contextualise strategies within the ethical and legal limitations of sharing Ground Truth.",
    "Because of these limitations and the urge to make people aware of the labour that is poured into data creation, the reuse of Ground Truth requires that contributions and contributors be acknowledged, which is discussed in the second section.",
    "In our conclusion, we combine and synthesize the two parts.",
    "This article is a proposal intended to start a discussion about how to conduct and acknowledge the work that goes into generating training data for machine learning."
  ]
}